OL,3,CEx-footballer Paul Ince banned from
OL,4,Croads after admitting drink-driving
OL,6,FThe 57-year-old former Manchester
OL,7,FUnited star was arrested at the scene
OL,8,Fand later charged with drink driving
OL,9,Fafter producing a reading of 49
OL,10,Fmicrogrammes of alcohol in 100
OL,11,Fmillilitres of breath.
OL,13,FNigel Jones, prosecuting, at Chester
OL,14,FCrown Court on Friday, 18 July, said:
OL,15,F"On the day in question, the defendant
OL,16,Fwas witnessed by an off-duty police
OL,17,Fofficer driving a vehicle perceived to
OL,18,Fbe swerving across the road."
