OL,3,CEx-footballer Paul Ince banned from
OL,4,Croads after admitting drink-driving
OL,6,FHe said the car swerved across the
OL,7,Fcentral reservation, hitting bollards
OL,8,Fand causing two tyres to burst. The
OL,9,Fcar then pulled into a petrol station
OL,10,Fwhere police officers attended.
OL,12,FFrank Rogers, defending, said: "My
OL,13,Fclient finds himself today facing the
OL,14,Fhuge impact of a ban, but he accepts
OL,15,Fhe only has himself to blame for that.
OL,16,FHe misjudged the fact he believed at
OL,17,Fthe time he would be under the limit."
