OL,3,CEx-footballer Paul Ince banned from
OL,4,Croads after admitting drink-driving
OL,6,FHe said: "The vehicle didn't collide
OL,7,Fwith the bollards. He's clipped both
OL,8,Fsides of the island, damaging tyres."
OL,10,FHe said an alert came up on the car
OL,11,Fabout the tyre pressure and Ince
OL,12,Fpulled into a garage where he
OL,13,Finspected the damage, called his wife
OL,14,Fand was about to call the Range Rover
OL,15,Fassist helpline when police arrived.
OL,17,FMr Rogers said Ince had been driving
OL,18,Ffor 39 years and had three points on
OL,19,Fhis licence.
