OL,3,CEx-footballer Paul Ince banned from
OL,4,Croads after admitting drink-driving
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Jack McGarva told Ince:
OL,7,F"The message has got to be if you're
OL,8,Fgoing to drive you don't drink at all."
OL,10,FHe was banned from driving for 12
OL,11,Fmonths, fined #5,000 and ordered to
OL,12,Fpay #2,000 and #85 costs.
OL,14,FThe two-time Premier League winner had
OL,15,Fa distinguished football career
OL,16,Fplaying for West Ham, Manchester
OL,17,FUnited, Inter Milan, Liverpool,
OL,18,FMiddlesbrough and Wolves from 1986 to
OL,19,F2007. He also won 53 caps for his
OL,20,Fcountry.
